### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### Current user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/me
Cookie: GIGSHIELD_SESSION={{sessionId}}

### Update profile
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: GIGSHIELD_SESSION={{sessionId}}

{
  "name": "Pavith",
  "phoneNumber": "9876543210",
  "city": "Chennai",
  "deliveryPlatform": "Swiggy",
  "vehicleType": "Bike",
  "aadhaarLast4": "4321"
}

### Available plans
GET http://localhost:8080/api/plans

### Subscribe to plan
POST http://localhost:8080/api/subscription
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: GIGSHIELD_SESSION={{sessionId}}

{
  "planCode": "STANDARD",
  "paymentReference": "mock-razorpay-standard"
}

### Active subscription
GET http://localhost:8080/api/subscription/me
Cookie: GIGSHIELD_SESSION={{sessionId}}
